# Together AI API Configuration
# Free tier: https://www.together.ai
# No Docker needed, instant deployment!

# Get your free API key:
# 1. Go to https://www.together.ai
# 2. Sign up for free account
# 3. Navigate to: Account → API Tokens
# 4. Copy your API token
# 5. Set it below

TOGETHER_API_KEY=your_api_key_here

# Local Development:
# 1. Create .env.local in project root
# 2. Add: TOGETHER_API_KEY=your_token_here
# 3. Run: npm run dev

# Production (Vercel):
# 1. Go to your Vercel project dashboard
# 2. Settings → Environment Variables
# 3. Add: TOGETHER_API_KEY = your_token_here
# 4. Redeploy project

